title: Gross Walenstock
text:
The Gross Walenstock is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> of the <a href="Urner%20Alps">Urner Alps</a>, located on the border between the cantons of <a href="Nidwalden">Nidwalden</a> and <a href="Obwalden">Obwalden</a> in <a href="Central%20Switzerland">Central Switzerland</a>. On its northern side it overlooks the <a href="Bannalpsee">Bannalpsee</a>.
The Gross Walenstock is part of the group named "Walenstöcke".
The closest localities are Oberrickenbach (Nidwalden) and <a href="Engelberg">Engelberg</a> (Obwalden).
